n{attr}`flask.Flask.permanent_session_lifetime` and if so, removes them.\n\nNote that no distinction is made between non-permanent and permanent\nsessions.\n\n```\nparam app\n\nThe app whose sessions should be cleaned up. If None,\nuses .\n```\n"]}, {"name": "docassemblekvsession.KVSessionExtension.init_app", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "app", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "session_kvstore", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Initialize application and KVSession.\n\nThis will replace the session management of the application with\nFlask-KVSession's.\n\n```\nparam app\n\nThe  app to be initialized.\n```\n"]}], "class_variables": [{"name": "docassemblekvsession.KVSessionExtension.key_regex", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": ["Activates Flask-KVSession for an application.\n\n```\nparam session_kvstore\n\nAn object supporting the\n interface that session\ndata will be store in.\n\nparam app\n\nThe app to activate. If not , this is essentially the\nsame as calling  later.\n```\n"]}], "exports": [{"name": "docassemblekvsession.BadSignature", "xref": {"fqname": "itsdangerous.BadSignature", "project": null}}, {"name": "docassemblekvsession.CallbackDict", "xref": {"fqname": "werkzeug.datastructures.CallbackDict", "project": null}}, {"name": "docassemblekvsession.current_app", "xref": {"fqname": "flask.current_app", "project": null}}, {"name": "docassemblekvsession.datetime", "xref": {"fqname": "datetime.datetime", "project": null}}, {"name": "docassemblekvsession.g", "xref": {"fqname": "flask.g", "project": null}}, {"name": "docassemblekvsession.SecureCookieSession", "xref": {"fqname": "flask.sessions.SecureCookieSession", "project": null}}, {"name": "docassemblekvsession.SessionInterface", "xref": {"fqname": "flask.sessions.SessionInterface", "project": null}}, {"name": "docassemblekvsession.Session